                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <cell><measureGrp><measure type="currency" unit="lb" quantity="2"
                                            >ij </measure>
                                        <measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="17"
                                            >xvij </measure></measureGrp></cell>
                                <cell>dem wirt umb <num value="18"
                                            >18</num> voggentzer brot per <measureGrp><measure
                                            type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="3">3 </measure>
                                        <measure type="currency" unit="h" quantity="2"
                                            >2 hlr</measure></measureGrp></cell>
                                <cell/>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <cell><measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="16"
                                        >xvj </measure></cell>
                                <cell>ouch imme umb <num value="2">2</num> hußbrot</cell>
                                <cell/>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <cell><measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="10"
                                    >x </measure></cell>
                                <cell>umb <num value="4">4</num> weggen</cell>
                                <cell/>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <cell><measureGrp><measure type="currency" unit="lb" quantity="35"
                                            >xxxv </measure>
                                        <measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="4"
                                            >iiij </measure></measureGrp></cell>
                                <cell>umb <measureGrp><measure type="volume" unit="Eimer"
                                            quantity="2" commodity="wine">2 eimer</measure>
                                        <measure type="volume" unit="Kopf" quantity="4"
                                            commodity="wine">4 <choice>
                                                <abbr>k</abbr>
                                                <expan>kopf</expan>
                                            </choice> wyn</measure></measureGrp> per <measure
                                        type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="11">11 </measure></cell>
                                <cell/>
                            </row></table>
<p><lb/>Summa deß aabent trunks ist <measureGrp><measure type="currency" unit="lb" quantity="55">lv </measure>
<measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="14"><add place="inline" rend="other ink">xij</add>ij </measure></measureGrp>,
<lb/>brüchte jeder person ongfar <measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="11">11 </measure> zuͦ ürten.</p>
<p><lb/>Darinnen sinnd die personen uss myner herren statt
<lb/>zuͦ gast ghalten worden. <add place="inline" rend="other ink">Dessglychen ouch <num value="8">8</num> personen <lb/>als die nüwen und alten richter.</add></p>
<p>
<lb/>Die pursamme dero <subst><del rend="strikethrough">72</del><add place="above" rend="other ink">64</add></subst> personen. Gibt jede zuͦ ürten <measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="5">5 </measure>.
<lb/>Bringt <subst><del rend="strikethrough"><measure type="currency" unit="lb" quantity="18">xviij </measure></del>
<add place="inline" rend="other ink"><measure type="currency" unit="lb" quantity="16">xvj </measure>.</add></subst></p>
<p>
<lb/>Nach abzug dessëlben, so blybt dann mynen herren
<lb/>zuͦbezalen im aabenttrunk
<lb/>an gëllt <measureGrp><measure type="currency" unit="lb" quantity="39">xxxvij<add place="inline" rend="other ink">ij</add> </measure>
<measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="14"><add place="inline" rend="other ink">xii</add>ij </measure></measureGrp>.</p>
<head type="subtitle">Wyter</head>
<table>
<row><cell><add place="inline" rend="other ink"><measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="10">x </measure></add></cell><cell><add place="inline" rend="other ink">umb eiger</add><note>Dieser Eintrag steht in der Reinschrift <bibl><ref target="https://suche.staatsarchiv.djiktzh.ch/detail.aspx?id=1119765">StAZH G I 5, Nr. 109</ref></bibl> nach Butter und Milch; eine geschweifte Klammer fasst alles <orig>zuͦ ankenbruten</orig> zusammen.</note></cell><cell/></row>
<row><cell><measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="8">viij </measure></cell><cell>inn stall</cell><cell><add place="inline" rend="other ink">hoffmeyer</add><note>Nach geschweifter Klammer um diese und vorherige Zeile.</note></cell></row>
<row><cell><measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="10">x </measure></cell><cell>den mägten</cell><cell><add place="inline" rend="other ink">hoffmeyers</add></cell></row>
<row><cell><add place="inline" rend="other ink"><measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="10">x </measure></add></cell><cell><add place="inline" rend="other ink">wirts magt</add></cell><cell/></row></table>
<p>
<lb/>Unnd dann den herren obervögten, gstiffts verordneten
<lb/>und schryber, jedem <measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="10">10 </measure> blonung und <measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="10">10 </measure> für rosslon.
<lb/>Thuͦt <measure type="currency" unit="lb" quantity="6">vj </measure>.<note>Hier endet die Abschrift <bibl><ref target="https://suche.staatsarchiv.djiktzh.ch/detail.aspx?id=1119765">StAZH G I 5, Nr. 109</ref></bibl>.</note>
<add place="inline" rend="other ink">Meer <measure type="currency" unit="lb" quantity="5">v </measure> bi der abrëchnung verzert.</add></p>
<head type="subtitle"> Summarum alles costens ist</head>
<p><lb/>an gëllt <measureGrp><measure type="currency" unit="lb" quantity="80">lxxx </measure>
<measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="12">xij </measure></measureGrp>.</p>
<p><lb/>Bringt mynen <abbr>g</abbr> herren und dem <orgName ref="org004352">gstifft</orgName> jedem theil
<lb/>an gëllt <measureGrp><measure type="currency" unit="lb" quantity="40">xl </measure>
<measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="6">vj </measure></measureGrp>.</p>
<p><lb/>Daran ist mynen herren an irem theil <measure type="currency" unit="lb" quantity="0"><unclear>0</unclear></measure> abgenommen,
<lb/>so das gstifft ouch gëben sol.</p>
<add place="left margin" rend="other ink"><p><lb/>Summa dem hoffmeyer <lb/><measureGrp><measure type="currency" unit="lb" quantity="26">xxvj </measure>
<measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="5">v </measure></measureGrp> zalt.</p><!-- Hier wurde zusammengezählt, was dem Hofmeier geschuldet wurde, aus dem Imbiss, dem Abendtrunk und den Nachträgen unter "Wyter". -->
<p><table><row><cell>Weybel</cell><cell><measureGrp><measure type="currency" unit="lb" quantity="59">lviiij </measure>
<measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="7">vij </measure></measureGrp></cell></row>
<row><cell>Daran empfacht er <lb/>von dorfflüthen</cell><cell><measure type="currency" unit="lb" quantity="16">xvj </measure></cell></row>
<row><cell>Rest</cell><cell><measureGrp><measure type="currency" unit="lb" quantity="43">xliij </measure>
<measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="7">vij </measure></measureGrp></cell></row></table>
<lb/>Daran empfacht er
<table><row><cell><measureGrp><measure type="currency" unit="lb" quantity="40">xl </measure>
<measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="6">vj </measure></measureGrp></cell><cell>vom hern ober<lb break="no"/>vogt</cell></row>
<row><cell><measureGrp><measure type="currency" unit="lb" quantity="3">iij </measure>
<measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="1">j </measure></measureGrp></cell><cell>vom <abbr>h</abbr> cammerer</cell></row></table></p></add>
</div>
