<div>
<ab type="dorsal" place="verso">
<lb/>Meyen grichts zuͦ <placeName ref="loc009768">Hönngg</placeName> costen
<lb/>verzeichnuß, anno <abbr>etc</abbr>
<date when="1597">97</date>.
</ab>
